A Design Guideline, also called a design principle or design heuristic,

00:00:04.920 --> 00:00:08.550
is an informal piece of advice about the structure of a design.

00:00:08.550 --> 00:00:11.720
With respect to objected-oriented designs,

00:00:11.720 --> 00:00:15.810
we are concerned with Design Guidelines that take the form of do's and

00:00:15.810 --> 00:00:19.580
don'ts. We will survey some of the most well known design principles. But

